Cell.Text: I already told you, I'm not going back to Solstheim.
If you're looking for passage to Solstheim, too bad. I'm not going back there any more.
If you're looking for passage to Solstheim, you won't find a finer vessel than the Northern Maiden.

Node.Caption: DLC2DRRGjalundInitBranchTopic: I need passage to Solstheim.

Cell.Text: I'll give you a fair price. Not many people headed over there these days. | If you ask me, I can't blame them. Things aren't what they used to be out there.

Node.Caption: DLC2DRRGjalundInitBranchTopic01: How much will it cost me?

Cell.Text: They still pay me for supplies and passage and I can always use the coin. | Still interested in heading over there?

Node.Caption: DLC2DRRGjalundInitBranchTopic03: Why sail there at all then?

Cell.Text: [S] G|You've got yourself a ship. We'll cast off immediately.
[S] G|I don't sail for free. Come back when you can actually pay me.

Node.Caption: DLC2DRRGjalundInitBranchTopic04: Yes. ( gold)

Cell.Text: [S] G|Suit yourself. I'll be here if you change your mind.

Node.Caption: DLC2DRRGjalundInitBranchTopic05: Not now.

Cell.Text: Surprised you've never heard of it. | It's an island northeast of here. Has a small dark elf town called Raven Rock and a handful of Nords living in Skaal Village. | People don't usually sail over there unless they have a particular reason. It can be a pretty rough place.

Node.Caption: DLC2DRRGjalundInitBranchTopic00: Solstheim?
DLC2DRRGjalundInitBranchTopicMQ01: You're the reason I was attacked by those cultists!
DLC2DRRGjalundInitBranchTopicMQ02: They threatened to kill you?
DLC2DRRGjalundInitBranchTopicMQ03: A voice in your head? Who was it?
DLC2DRRGjalundInitBranchTopicMQ04

Cell.Text: Sure. Yeah. That's me. Why? Who sent you?

Node.Caption: DLC2DRRGjalundMQIntroA1: Are you the captain of the Northern Maiden?

Cell.Text: Surprised you've never heard of it. | It's an island northeast of here. Has a small dark elf town called Raven Rock and a handful of Nords living in Skaal Village. | But I'm not going back there. There's something wrong about that place.

Node.Caption: DLC2DRRGjalundMQIntroB1: Solstheim? Where's that?

Cell.Text: <<Shared>> It's hard to explain... I remember those creepy cultist fellows coming on board, then... | Next thing I remember, I was here and they were gone. That's not right, losing whole days like that.

Node.Caption: DLC2DRRGjalundMQIntroB2: What happened? Why won't you go back?

Cell.Text: Now hold on! That wasn't my fault... I didn't know they were going to attack anybody. I don't even know how I got here.

Node.Caption: DLC2DRRGjalundMQIntroA2: I was attacked by some cultists who came here on your ship.

Cell.Text: <<Shared>> It's hard to explain... I remember those creepy cultist fellows coming on board, then... | Next thing I remember, I was here and they were gone. That's not right, losing whole days like that.

Node.Caption: DLC2DRRGjalundMQIntroA3: How can you not know how you got here? You sailed here, right?

Cell.Text: Have you been listening to me? I'm not going back there.

Node.Caption: DLC2DRRGjalundMQIntroC1: Yes, you are. You're taking me to Solstheim.

Cell.Text: There's been something strange going on there for a while, but this... this is something else. I hope you get to the bottom of it.
[S] <<Shared>> There's been something strange going on there for a while, but after this... I'm done. I'm not going back to Solstheim.

Node.Caption: DLC2DRRGjalundMQIntroB3: What happened?

Cell.Text: [S] G|Well... a man's got to make a living, after all. Fine. We'll cast off immediately.
That's a tempting offer... when you actually have the gold, I might be willing to consider it.

Node.Caption: DLC2DRRGjalundMQIntroBribe: I'll pay you double your usual rate. (Give gold)

Cell.Text: [S] Alright, you have a point. Taking you back to find out who sent them is the least I can do. | Besides, maybe you can put a stop to whatever's going on over there. I owe them a bit of payback myself.
Look, I'm sorry about your troubles, but I've got to look out for myself. I'm not going to risk it.

Node.Caption: DLC2DRRGjalundMQIntroPersuade: You owe me. You brought those cultists here. (Persuade)

Cell.Text: [S] G|Hold on, now. I'm just a simple sailor. I never wanted to get mixed up in any of this. Alright, I'll take you. But we leave immediately.
Yeah, well, and I don't want them trying to kill me. So the answer is still no.

Node.Caption: DLC2DRRGjalundMQIntroIntimidate: People are trying to kill me. I'm not taking no for an answer. (Intimidate)

Cell.Text: G|Whatever you want. The answer isn't going to be any different later though.

Node.Caption: DLC2DRRGjalundMQIntroNotNot: I'll be back.
